00:28:48,700 --> 00:28:50,710
suspicious of your parents?

566
00:28:57,300 --> 00:28:58,960
You haven't seen each other for 10 years.

567
00:28:58,960 --> 00:29:00,420
It's normal that there's a feeling

568
00:29:00,420 --> 00:29:01,500
of estrangement.

569
00:29:03,500 --> 00:29:04,900
We've been apart for too long.

570
00:29:04,900 --> 00:29:07,070
I should cherish every moment of reunion,

571
00:29:07,070 --> 00:29:08,770
but I don't feel natural intimacy

572
00:29:08,770 --> 00:29:10,610
from my heart toward them.

573
00:29:11,790 --> 00:29:12,590
Do you think it's my problem

574
00:29:12,590 --> 00:29:13,510
or theirs?

575
00:29:17,400 --> 00:29:18,070
Zhao,

576
00:29:18,070 --> 00:29:18,870
Ms. Fu Ling.

577
00:29:18,900 --> 00:29:20,470
Come in and eat.

578
00:29:20,510 --> 00:29:21,510
Coming.

579
00:29:28,720 --> 00:29:29,330
Here,

580
00:29:29,360 --> 00:29:30,000
Ms. Fu Ling.

581
00:29:30,000 --> 00:29:30,680
Thank you.

582
00:29:32,060 --> 00:29:32,990
Eat, Zhao.

583
00:29:39,990 --> 00:29:40,710
Zhao,

584
00:29:40,740 --> 00:29:41,840
why aren't you eating?

585
00:29:41,840 --> 00:29:44,080
Do you not like my cooking?

586
00:29:44,930 --> 00:29:45,580
No.

587
00:29:46,260 --> 00:29:48,060
I found heavy fog in the mountain

588
00:29:48,080 --> 00:29:49,780
and it blocked the way out of the village.

589
00:29:49,780 --> 00:29:51,480
Do you know what this is?

590
00:29:52,930 --> 00:29:54,010
Heavy fog?

591
00:29:54,460 --> 00:29:57,010
Maybe it's because of the bad weather.

592
00:29:58,710 --> 00:30:00,430
Why? Are you leaving?

593
00:30:01,330 --> 00:30:03,120
Chong Zhao just reunited with you.

594
00:30:03,120 --> 00:30:04,600
How could he bear to leave?

595
00:30:05,160 --> 00:30:06,190
That's good.

596
00:30:06,220 --> 00:30:07,220
That's good.

597
00:30:08,020 --> 00:30:09,350
-Let’s eat.
-Let’s eat.

598
00:30:11,880 --> 00:30:13,630
Do you really want us to stay?

599
00:30:14,890 --> 00:30:16,810
What are you talking about?

600
00:30:16,880 --> 00:30:18,680
Your mother and I haven't seen you for 10 years.

601
00:30:18,680 --> 00:30:19,820
Now we finally meet again.

602
00:30:19,820 --> 00:30:21,760
Of course we hope to spend more time with you.

603
00:30:21,760 --> 00:30:23,410
Why don't we go together?

604
00:30:23,440 --> 00:30:25,380
Going back to Lanling or Ning'an City,

605
00:30:25,380 --> 00:30:26,460
you can still hide your identity

606
00:30:26,460 --> 00:30:27,920
and live an ordinary life.

607
00:30:31,720 --> 00:30:32,610
Zhao,

608
00:30:32,640 --> 00:30:34,960
your father and I have lived here for 10 years.

609
00:30:34,960 --> 00:30:35,940
We're used to it.

610
00:30:35,960 --> 00:30:36,990
We don't want the trouble anymore.

611
00:30:36,990 --> 00:30:38,200
You were in Lanling for 100 years,

612
00:30:38,200 --> 00:30:39,390
but you could give it up easily.

613
00:30:39,390 --> 00:30:40,590
You've only lived here for 10 years.

614
00:30:40,590 --> 00:30:41,310
Why...

615
00:30:41,310 --> 00:30:42,510
What can't you let go?

616
00:30:42,920 --> 00:30:44,650
Or are you afraid of something?

617
00:30:47,480 --> 00:30:48,150
Mother,

618
00:30:48,880 --> 00:30:50,200
you met Bai Xi when you were

619
00:30:50,200 --> 00:30:51,240
running away back then, right?

620
00:30:51,240 --> 00:30:51,830
Why did you ask her to tell me

621
00:30:51,830 --> 00:30:53,680
not to go back to Lanling?

622
00:30:53,710 --> 00:30:55,400
Who is after you?

623
00:30:55,420 --> 00:30:57,410
Which sect? Which group? Who?

624
00:30:59,510 --> 00:31:00,830
You won't forget the enemy that

625
00:31:00,830 --> 00:31:01,910
wanted to kill you, right?

626
00:31:01,910 --> 00:31:02,910
Father.

627
00:31:02,930 --> 00:31:04,240
You and Master were close.

628
00:31:04,240 --> 00:31:05,400
Does Master know you're hiding in

629
00:31:05,400 --> 00:31:06,390
Bodhi Village?

630
00:31:08,740 --> 00:31:09,740
Chong Zhao.

631
00:31:11,650 --> 00:31:13,450
So what do you mean?

632
00:31:14,000 --> 00:31:15,580
Do you know what you're doing?

633
00:31:15,580 --> 00:31:17,260
You're interrogating your parents.

634
00:31:17,260 --> 00:31:18,640
You're doubting your Master.

635
00:31:18,640 --> 00:31:20,220
I just want to know the truth.

636
00:31:20,220 --> 00:31:22,540
How did your mother and I teach you?

637
00:31:22,560 --> 00:31:23,890
It's only been 10 years.

638
00:31:24,210 --> 00:31:26,710
Have you forgotten the most basic filial piety?

639
00:31:26,710 --> 00:31:28,070
I'm so angry.

640
00:31:32,840 --> 00:31:34,740
Why are you mad at him?

641
00:31:40,290 --> 00:31:41,120
Enough.

642
00:31:41,150 --> 00:31:42,300
Stop pretending.

643
00:31:43,500 --> 00:31:44,720
He's already suspicious.

644
00:31:44,720 --> 00:31:45,590
What should we do now?

645
00:31:45,590 --> 00:31:46,960
Don't be nervous. The Divine Maiden said

646
00:31:46,960 --> 00:31:48,270
it's normal for them to be suspicious.

647
00:31:48,270 --> 00:31:49,750
As long as she's not angry,

648
00:31:49,770 --> 00:31:51,170
everything will be fine.

649
00:31:52,330 --> 00:31:54,790
I hope the Divine Maiden can get what she wants soon.

650
00:31:54,790 --> 00:31:56,210
Only when she is happy

651
00:31:56,240 --> 00:31:58,020
can our lives be easier.

652
00:32:06,620 --> 00:32:08,690
I know you have a lot of doubts,

653
00:32:08,720 --> 00:32:11,110
but you were too emotional just now.

654
00:32:11,820 --> 00:32:13,550
I didn't want to get emotional,

655
00:32:14,020 --> 00:32:15,550
but I couldn't help it.

656
00:32:15,850 --> 00:32:18,460
I wish everything can go back to how it was.

657
00:32:19,210 --> 00:32:21,680
But why is it the more I ask, the more wrong it feels?

658
00:32:21,680 --> 00:32:22,960
My father used to teach me

659
00:32:22,960 --> 00:32:24,430
to persuade people with reason,

660
00:32:24,430 --> 00:32:26,300
instead of volume and status.

661
00:32:26,530 --> 00:32:29,190
But he threatened me with filial piety just now.

662
00:32:29,500 --> 00:32:31,220
He's trying to avoid things.

663
00:32:32,260 --> 00:32:35,590
Maybe there's a natural instinct when facing one's family.

664
00:32:35,740 --> 00:32:36,610
I think

665
00:32:37,630 --> 00:32:39,060
they are not my parents.

666
00:32:40,190 --> 00:32:41,670
But if they are fake,

667
00:32:41,690 --> 00:32:43,210
why would they do that?

668
00:32:43,230 --> 00:32:44,300
And why do they

669
00:32:44,330 --> 00:32:46,130
look exactly like your parents?

670
00:32:47,160 --> 00:32:48,730
I've observed them these days.

671
00:32:48,730 --> 00:32:49,850
The two of them

672
00:32:49,880 --> 00:32:51,310
are not disguised

673
00:32:51,530 --> 00:32:53,390
nor created with Eternal power.

674
00:32:54,880 --> 00:32:58,540
Have you heard that there was a secret technique in ancient times?

675
00:32:58,780 --> 00:33:00,050
Called puppetry.

676
00:33:18,110 --> 00:33:19,420
No trespassing

677
00:33:19,450 --> 00:33:20,840
the Divine Maiden's room.

678
00:33:20,840 --> 00:33:21,910
Who are you?

679
00:33:21,930 --> 00:33:23,510
I'm the only doctor in Bodhi Village,

680
00:33:23,400 --> 00:33:25,340
[Qin Jiang, doctor of Bodhi Village]

681
00:33:23,510 --> 00:33:24,420
Qin Jiang.

682
00:33:24,450 --> 00:33:25,400
The Divine Maiden is sick.

683
00:33:25,400 --> 00:33:26,630
She won't see any guests for now.

684
00:33:26,630 --> 00:33:27,630
Please leave.

685
00:33:27,660 --> 00:33:28,460
Sick?

686
00:33:28,840 --> 00:33:29,840
Coincidentally,

687
00:33:30,400 --> 00:33:32,030
there are many elixirs in Bright Moon Palace.

688
00:33:32,030 --> 00:33:34,560
Let me see what ailment she has

689
00:33:34,580 --> 00:33:35,840
so that I can treat her.

690
00:33:43,460 --> 00:33:45,600
She just fell asleep after taking the medicine.

691
00:33:45,600 --> 00:33:46,920
Please leave.

692
00:33:59,550 --> 00:34:02,770
Fan Yue!

693
00:34:04,290 --> 00:34:05,850
What's wrong with her?

694
00:34:05,870 --> 00:34:07,210
The Bodhi Village

695
00:34:07,230 --> 00:34:08,750
is protected by the Divine Maiden.

696
00:34:08,750 --> 00:34:12,120
All the food and water in the village are made by the Divine Maiden.

697
00:34:12,120 --> 00:34:14,020
She used too much of her spiritual power

698
00:34:14,020 --> 00:34:15,370
and needs to sleep and rest.

699
00:34:15,370 --> 00:34:16,850
She will wake up in a few days.

700
00:34:16,850 --> 00:34:18,080
So,

701
00:34:18,100 --> 00:34:20,159
she set up the fog around the village?

702
00:34:20,210 --> 00:34:22,320
She knew she was going to fall into deep slumber.

703
00:34:22,320 --> 00:34:23,360
She was worried that

704
00:34:23,360 --> 00:34:25,510
something would happen in Bodhi Village without her protection.

705
00:34:25,510 --> 00:34:26,880
That's why she set up the fog

706
00:34:26,880 --> 00:34:28,340
to stop people from entering and exiting.

707
00:34:28,340 --> 00:34:30,239
The Divine Maiden did this for the sake of the villagers.

708
00:34:30,239 --> 00:34:31,480
When she wakes up a few days later,

709
00:34:31,480 --> 00:34:32,840
she'll undo the fog.

710
00:34:33,210 --> 00:34:34,210
But now,

711
00:34:34,230 --> 00:34:35,500
please leave.

712
00:34:35,530 --> 00:34:37,429
Don't disturb her rest.

713
00:34:40,960 --> 00:34:41,730
Fan Yue.

714
00:34:41,750 --> 00:34:42,810
Don't believe her.

715
00:34:46,070 --> 00:34:47,110
Fan Yue!

716
00:34:51,110 --> 00:34:52,150
Fan Yue.

717
00:34:57,250 --> 00:34:59,370
Your power and divine soul have been imprisoned

718
00:34:59,370 --> 00:35:00,870
by the Divine Maiden.

719
00:35:01,250 --> 00:35:02,880
No matter how loudly you shout,

720
00:35:02,880 --> 00:35:04,110
he won't hear you.

721
00:35:04,130 --> 00:35:06,070
Just lie there obediently.

722
00:35:22,780 --> 00:35:24,440
How did it go?

723
00:35:25,890 --> 00:35:27,240
Luan Zhu is sleeping.

724
00:35:27,270 --> 00:35:28,790
She'll wake up in a few days.

725
00:35:28,790 --> 00:35:29,970
Do you believe it?

726
00:35:30,620 --> 00:35:31,290
No.

727
00:35:32,510 --> 00:35:34,160
With your personality,

728
00:35:34,180 --> 00:35:36,120
you should've gotten to the bottom of things.

729
00:35:36,120 --> 00:35:37,950
Why did you come back?

730
00:35:37,970 --> 00:35:39,180
Could it be

731
00:35:39,210 --> 00:35:41,630
you still care about your relationship with her 60,000 years ago?

732
00:35:41,630 --> 00:35:42,310
No.

733
00:35:42,340 --> 00:35:43,240
I know.

734
00:35:43,690 --> 00:35:44,850
I'm just kidding.

735
00:35:46,370 --> 00:35:47,490
It's getting late.

736
00:35:47,510 --> 00:35:48,720
Go to bed early.

737
00:35:48,750 --> 00:35:50,060
We can resolve

738
00:35:50,080 --> 00:35:51,810
tomorrow's matters tomorrow.

739
00:36:02,080 --> 00:36:04,480
This is your first time helping me undress.

740
00:36:06,770 --> 00:36:07,770
Isn't it good?

741
00:36:08,620 --> 00:36:09,500
It's okay.

742
00:36:09,650 --> 00:36:10,750
I can do it myself.

743
00:36:16,700 --> 00:36:17,780
He's here.

744
00:36:18,490 --> 00:36:19,960
I suddenly remembered

745
00:36:20,670 --> 00:36:22,440
Master hasn't taken his medicine tonight.

746
00:36:22,440 --> 00:36:23,850
I'll go check on him.

747
00:36:24,350 --> 00:36:25,640
Get some rest.

748
00:36:25,670 --> 00:36:27,190
I'll be back soon.

749
00:36:53,590 --> 00:36:55,560
Sect Leader, do you want to kill me?

750
00:36:57,850 --> 00:36:59,580
What do you think about

751
00:37:00,090 --> 00:37:01,170
my new skin?

752
00:37:05,560 --> 00:37:07,010
Divine Maiden,

753
00:37:07,040 --> 00:37:08,730
did Fan Yue notice that

754
00:37:08,750 --> 00:37:10,900
you took Bai Shuo's body?

755
00:37:10,930 --> 00:37:12,050
What?

756
00:37:12,070 --> 00:37:13,950
Are you questioning my ability?

757
00:37:13,970 --> 00:37:14,860
I dare not.

758
00:37:14,890 --> 00:37:16,710
You are all-powerful.

759
00:37:16,730 --> 00:37:18,000
I’m just curious

760
00:37:18,030 --> 00:37:20,110
how you switched bodies with Bai Shuo

761
00:37:20,130 --> 00:37:21,920
without anyone knowing?

762
00:37:21,940 --> 00:37:23,190
Don't ask

763
00:37:23,220 --> 00:37:24,660
what you shouldn't ask.

764
00:37:24,890 --> 00:37:27,330
Divine Maiden, why did you suddenly

765
00:37:27,350 --> 00:37:28,420
summon me here today?

766
00:37:28,420 --> 00:37:30,270
I exchanged bodies with Bai Shuo

767
00:37:30,290 --> 00:37:31,880
and used up a lot of spiritual power.

768
00:37:31,880 --> 00:37:33,260
I need some nourishment.

769
00:37:33,260 --> 00:37:35,280
Send some new Eternals in.

770
00:37:37,460 --> 00:37:38,540
You're unwilling?

771
00:37:40,880 --> 00:37:41,920
Back then,

772
00:37:41,950 --> 00:37:44,570
Fan Yue came to our sect to steal the Contemplation Stone.

773
00:37:44,570 --> 00:37:46,340
I deliberately didn't stop him

774
00:37:46,370 --> 00:37:47,440
just to use him

775
00:37:47,440 --> 00:37:49,610
to help me find someone who can gather the Five Contemplations.

776
00:37:49,610 --> 00:37:51,870
Now, Bai Shuo has gathered four Contemplations.

777
00:37:51,870 --> 00:37:53,680
We're one step away from success.

778
00:37:53,680 --> 00:37:55,690
If you take her body now,

779
00:37:55,720 --> 00:37:57,640
the Five Contemplations won't be gathered.

780
00:37:57,640 --> 00:37:59,010
If we don't gather all five,

781
00:37:59,010 --> 00:38:01,690
we can't activate the power of the divine stone.

782
00:38:01,720 --> 00:38:03,860
All I want is Fan Yue.

783
00:38:03,880 --> 00:38:06,360
I don't care if the Contemplation Stone

784
00:38:06,380 --> 00:38:07,970
can be activated or not.

785
00:38:08,690 --> 00:38:09,860
Jin Yao,

786
00:38:09,890 --> 00:38:12,430
these years, I've taught you the secret mental cultivation methods,

787
00:38:12,430 --> 00:38:14,150
helped you cultivate with spiritual power,

788
00:38:14,150 --> 00:38:16,410
and made you the leader of the Eternals.

789
00:38:16,430 --> 00:38:18,320
You've gotten enough.

790
00:38:18,350 --> 00:38:19,730
You're still not satisfied?

791
00:38:19,730 --> 00:38:22,660
