792
00:38:22,710 --> 00:38:23,880
Those who are too greedy

793
00:38:23,880 --> 00:38:25,710
don't meet good endings.

794
00:38:25,770 --> 00:38:27,650
Stay in your place.

795
00:38:27,670 --> 00:38:30,580
Don't forget that I gave you everything you have today.

796
00:38:30,580 --> 00:38:32,570
I can take it back anytime.

797
00:39:07,530 --> 00:39:09,600
Do you really want to die?

798
00:39:11,320 --> 00:39:12,030
Who is it?

799
00:39:17,640 --> 00:39:19,470
You can hear my voice?

800
00:39:19,740 --> 00:39:21,060
For so many years,

801
00:39:21,090 --> 00:39:22,480
you're the first one.

802
00:39:23,800 --> 00:39:24,910
Stop looking.

803
00:39:24,930 --> 00:39:26,430
I'm right in front of you.

804
00:39:28,400 --> 00:39:30,000
What demonic object are you?

805
00:39:30,420 --> 00:39:31,310
Demon?

806
00:39:44,670 --> 00:39:46,450
Do you really want to die?

807
00:39:46,550 --> 00:39:47,550
If you do,

808
00:39:47,580 --> 00:39:48,840
I can help you.

809
00:39:50,640 --> 00:39:52,120
Why don't you answer?

810
00:39:52,150 --> 00:39:53,390
You don't want to answer

811
00:39:53,390 --> 00:39:54,700
or do you not dare to?

812
00:39:54,720 --> 00:39:56,080
You don't dare to die

813
00:39:56,130 --> 00:39:57,450
nor do you want to die.

814
00:40:01,290 --> 00:40:02,640
Who are you?

815
00:40:03,100 --> 00:40:04,490
I'm not a demon

816
00:40:04,520 --> 00:40:05,880
nor an eternal.

817
00:40:06,220 --> 00:40:07,850
You should know

818
00:40:07,870 --> 00:40:10,200
there once was a Divine Race.

819
00:40:10,230 --> 00:40:11,340
Divine Race?

820
00:40:11,660 --> 00:40:12,560
You are...

821
00:40:31,920 --> 00:40:32,960
Jin Yao,

822
00:40:32,980 --> 00:40:34,670
I know everything about you.

823
00:40:34,700 --> 00:40:35,810
Your parents died young

824
00:40:35,810 --> 00:40:37,250
and your family was poor.

825
00:40:37,270 --> 00:40:39,630
You worked so hard to leave Bodhi Village

826
00:40:39,660 --> 00:40:41,530
and joined the Lanling Sect,

827
00:40:41,550 --> 00:40:44,140
but you were always oppressed by your peers because of your humble background.

828
00:40:44,140 --> 00:40:45,620
You were humiliated.

829
00:40:45,640 --> 00:40:46,950
You're in pain,

830
00:40:46,980 --> 00:40:48,150
right?

831
00:40:48,710 --> 00:40:50,350
Why?

832
00:40:50,380 --> 00:40:53,480
Why do some people have everything when they are born?

833
00:40:53,510 --> 00:40:55,070
I tried my best,

834
00:40:55,090 --> 00:40:57,070
but I still couldn't get a slightly fair chance.

835
00:40:57,070 --> 00:40:59,320
There is no fairness in this world.

836
00:40:59,340 --> 00:41:00,850
If you want to rise above others,

837
00:41:00,850 --> 00:41:01,960
I can help you.

838
00:41:01,980 --> 00:41:03,710
I can give you power,

839
00:41:03,740 --> 00:41:05,320
help you gain a foothold in Lanling,

840
00:41:05,320 --> 00:41:06,800
help you become the leader of the Eternals,

841
00:41:06,800 --> 00:41:09,540
and help you take revenge on those who bullied you.

842
00:41:09,540 --> 00:41:11,520
Whether it's a sinister and despicable Senior,

843
00:41:11,520 --> 00:41:13,440
or the unfair Master,

