00:41:13,470 --> 00:41:14,920
as long as you want,

845
00:41:14,940 --> 00:41:17,220
they will all disappear from this world.

846
00:41:21,590 --> 00:41:23,790
Don't you want such a good opportunity?

847
00:41:24,460 --> 00:41:25,780
If not,

848
00:41:26,440 --> 00:41:27,400
then forget it.

849
00:41:27,430 --> 00:41:28,110
Wait.

850
00:41:29,510 --> 00:41:30,790
What's the condition?

851
00:41:31,410 --> 00:41:33,260
What do you want me to do?

852
00:41:33,280 --> 00:41:35,480
60,000 years ago in the war of the Divine Region,

853
00:41:35,480 --> 00:41:36,850
my spiritual soul was damaged.

854
00:41:36,850 --> 00:41:38,550
I was in deep slumber until now.

855
00:41:38,550 --> 00:41:40,440
I need to absorb the spiritual energy of Eternals

856
00:41:40,440 --> 00:41:42,260
to maintain a human form.

857
00:41:42,280 --> 00:41:45,290
You just need to give some Eternals to me regularly.

858
00:41:47,860 --> 00:41:49,340
It's just a little favor.

859
00:41:49,370 --> 00:41:51,480
I don't need you to sacrifice anything.

860
00:41:51,480 --> 00:41:52,870
You just need to

861
00:41:53,660 --> 00:41:55,830
forget your conscience.

862
00:41:56,040 --> 00:41:57,360
That's all.

863
00:42:05,480 --> 00:42:06,740
I will

864
00:42:06,770 --> 00:42:08,320
always remember your kindness.

865
00:42:08,320 --> 00:42:10,250
I dare not have improper thoughts.

866
00:42:10,270 --> 00:42:11,890
But there is one more thing

867
00:42:11,910 --> 00:42:13,200
I need your help with.

868
00:42:13,230 --> 00:42:14,110
What is it?

869
00:42:14,590 --> 00:42:15,920
When I was capturing

870
00:42:15,920 --> 00:42:17,720
Chong Tai and Meng Ning back then,

871
00:42:17,720 --> 00:42:21,120
I accidentally met Bai Shuo's sister, Bai Xi.

872
00:42:27,080 --> 00:42:28,040
Father!

873
00:42:28,070 --> 00:42:30,330
I'm going to get Father to save Aunt Meng.

874
00:42:52,050 --> 00:42:55,220
Back then, Bai Xi was just a human child.

875
00:42:55,250 --> 00:42:57,750
She didn't die after being hit by me twice

876
00:42:58,030 --> 00:43:00,170
and became the current Fu Ling.

877
00:43:01,750 --> 00:43:03,990
She didn't die after two strikes?

878
00:43:04,010 --> 00:43:05,530
Interesting.

879
00:43:05,560 --> 00:43:06,480
I'm not sure

880
00:43:06,480 --> 00:43:08,670
if she saw my face or not.

881
00:43:09,330 --> 00:43:12,030
Divine Maiden, please kill Fu Ling and Chong Zhao

882
00:43:12,030 --> 00:43:13,840
in Bodhi Village.

883
00:43:14,860 --> 00:43:16,710
Killing Fu Ling isn't strange,

884
00:43:16,790 --> 00:43:19,300
but Chong Zhao is your personal disciple.

885
00:43:19,330 --> 00:43:20,730
You've been his teacher for years.

886
00:43:20,730 --> 00:43:22,110
Can you bear to be heartless?

887
00:43:22,110 --> 00:43:24,030
He already suspects me.

888
00:43:24,050 --> 00:43:25,910
If he must be killed, then so be it.

889
00:43:26,510 --> 00:43:28,360
Sometimes I'm quite curious.

890
00:43:28,380 --> 00:43:30,000
If the world's Eternals found out

891
00:43:30,000 --> 00:43:31,290
that their leader

892
00:43:31,310 --> 00:43:33,360
is such a ruthless

893
00:43:33,390 --> 00:43:35,110
and sinful person,

894
00:43:35,130 --> 00:43:36,600
how would they react?

895
00:43:38,540 --> 00:43:39,740
I have other things to do.

896
00:43:39,740 --> 00:43:41,100
Go back first.

897
00:43:41,120 --> 00:43:42,720
I have my own considerations

898
00:43:42,750 --> 00:43:44,310
for Bodhi Village's matters.

899
00:43:44,310 --> 00:43:45,780
You don't need to intervene

900
00:43:45,780 --> 00:43:47,340
or ask about it.

901
00:43:47,360 --> 00:43:47,950
Yes.

902
00:43:47,980 --> 00:43:49,870
I'll do as you say, Divine Maiden.

903
00:44:45,980 --> 00:44:48,140
Why do I always feel that you are

904
00:44:49,520 --> 00:44:51,430
different from before?

